sql: SELECT Minister FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE  Region_ID <= 79 ORDER BY Minister ASC
SELECT Member_in_charge_ID FROM party_events WHERE  Member_in_charge_ID > 96 ORDER BY Member_in_charge_ID DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT region.Region_ID, Format, Region_name FROM party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID WHERE party.Region_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 4
SELECT n.Member_ID, n.In_office FROM member AS n WHERE  n.Member_ID >= 18 GROUP BY n.In_office
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT party.Party_ID), party.Region_ID FROM party AS g JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = g.Party_ID GROUP BY party.Region_ID HAVING SUM(g.Party_ID) <= 15

SELECT SUM(party_events.Party_ID), Event_ID FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE party_events.Party_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM member AS b WHERE  b.Member_ID >= 60 AND party_events.Event_ID = b.Member_ID) ORDER BY Event_ID DESC
SELECT Took_office, Event_Name FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE  party_events.Party_ID != 68 GROUP BY Event_Name ORDER BY Event_Name DESC
SELECT AVG(Region_ID), Region_ID, Region_ID FROM region WHERE Region_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Region_ID <= 57 LIMIT 1

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Format), Member_Name FROM member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID WHERE  region.Region_ID >= 39 GROUP BY Member_Name
SELECT Event_ID FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE Region_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Event_ID != 26 ORDER BY Event_ID DESC

SELECT Member_in_charge_ID, Party_name, Took_office, In_office FROM party_events JOIN member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID AND party_events.Member_in_charge_ID = member.Member_ID WHERE Member_in_charge_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY In_office ORDER BY Party_name DESC
SELECT Member_ID, Member_ID, Party_ID FROM member WHERE Member_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY Party_ID ORDER BY Member_ID ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT Region_ID, Region_ID FROM region WHERE  Region_ID = 66 LIMIT 4
SELECT d.Event_ID, d.Event_Name FROM party_events AS d WHERE  d.Event_ID < 72 GROUP BY d.Event_Name HAVING MIN(d.Member_in_charge_ID) < 87 LIMIT 8

SELECT Party_ID, Took_office FROM party WHERE Region_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Party_name > (SELECT SUM(Party_name) FROM party AS b WHERE b.Party_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY Took_office HAVING COUNT(Party_ID) < 66 LIMIT 1
SELECT Region_ID, party_events.Party_ID, Party_name FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE  party.Party_ID = 55
SELECT MIN(party.Region_ID), COUNT(party.Region_ID) FROM party AS n JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = n.Party_ID WHERE  n.Region_ID != 59
SELECT t.Format FROM region AS t WHERE  t.Region_ID <= 85 GROUP BY t.Format HAVING MIN(t.Region_ID) = 49
SELECT Region_ID FROM party_events JOIN party ON party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE  Region_ID = 88

SELECT AVG(party.Party_ID), SUM(region.Region_ID), Format FROM party_events JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID WHERE Minister <= (SELECT AVG(Minister) FROM party AS n) GROUP BY Format HAVING AVG(party_events.Party_ID) < 21

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT party.Region_ID), Catalogue, Member_in_charge_ID FROM party_events JOIN member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID AND party_events.Member_in_charge_ID = member.Member_ID WHERE Member_in_charge_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Member_ID = 68 GROUP BY Member_in_charge_ID ORDER BY Member_in_charge_ID DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.Member_Name), p.In_office FROM member AS p WHERE  p.Member_ID >= 10 ORDER BY p.In_office ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT MIN(Party_ID), Event_ID FROM party_events WHERE Party_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Party_ID = (SELECT AVG(Party_ID) FROM party WHERE Region_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Party_ID >= 4 LIMIT 5) LIMIT 6

SELECT MAX(party.Region_ID), MIN(region.Region_ID), member.Party_ID FROM member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID GROUP BY member.Party_ID HAVING MAX(Member_ID) <= 99

SELECT party.Region_ID FROM party_events JOIN member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID AND party_events.Member_in_charge_ID = member.Member_ID ORDER BY party.Region_ID DESC LIMIT 6
SELECT MAX(Party_ID), Catalogue FROM party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID WHERE  party.Region_ID = 87 ORDER BY Catalogue DESC LIMIT 7
SELECT Catalogue, party.Region_ID FROM party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID WHERE  party.Region_ID = 15 GROUP BY party.Region_ID ORDER BY Catalogue DESC
SELECT MAX(Party_ID), MIN(Region_ID), Region_ID FROM party WHERE  Region_ID >= 69 GROUP BY Region_ID HAVING MIN(Party_ID) > 33 ORDER BY Region_ID DESC
SELECT Party_ID FROM party_events WHERE Event_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Member_in_charge_ID IN (SELECT Member_in_charge_ID FROM party_events AS b WHERE  b.Member_in_charge_ID != 92) LIMIT 2

SELECT MIN(party.Region_ID), member.Party_ID FROM party_events JOIN member JOIN party JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID AND party.Party_ID = party_events.Party_ID AND member.Party_ID = party.Party_ID AND party_events.Member_in_charge_ID = member.Member_ID WHERE  member.Party_ID >= 10 GROUP BY member.Party_ID HAVING AVG(party_events.Party_ID) >= 16 LIMIT 1
SELECT Member_ID, Party_ID, In_office FROM member WHERE Member_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY In_office HAVING COUNT(Member_ID) = 35

SELECT Party_name, Took_office, Region_ID FROM party WHERE Party_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Took_office IN (SELECT Took_office FROM party AS f WHERE  f.Region_ID >= 15) GROUP BY Region_ID HAVING MIN(Region_ID) >= 77
